  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You bestow lupine traits on a group of living creatures that you designate within range. Choose one of the following benefits to be gained by all targets for the duration:<ul><li><em><strong>Thick Fur.</strong></em> Each target sprouts fur over its entire body, giving it a +2 bonus to Armor Class.</li><li><em><strong>Keen Hearing and Smell.</strong></em> Each target has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on hearing or smell.</li><li><em><strong>Pack Tactics.</strong></em> Each affected creature has advantage on an attack roll against a target if at least one of the attacker’s allies (also under the effect of this spell) is within 5 feet of the target of the attack and the ally isn’t incapacitated.</li><br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the duration increases by 1 minute for each slot level above 3rd.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
